---
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";
import lifeInAustralia from "@assets/img/life-in-australia.jpg";
---

<div class="container mt-120">
  <div class="life-container">
    <div class="image-section col-12 col-md-6">
      <Image src={lifeInAustralia} alt="Life in USA" />
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6" style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-direction: column; ">
      <div class="text-section">
        <h2>Life in USA</h2>
        <p style="">
For students, living in the United States is an exciting journey full of learning, development, and exploration opportunities. Students have a plethora of options for broadening their interests, including participating in a variety of extracurricular activities and taking classes at prestigious universities. They can learn about American culture, have fun, and make friendships that will last a lifetime with people from all over the world.        </p>
        <a href="#" class="button">Find out more</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
      .life-container {
        max-height: 400px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        background-color: #0d5ba4;
        color: white;
      }
      .image-section img {
        max-width: 100%;
        height: 400px;
      }

      .text-section {
        padding:;
        max-width: 400px;
      }

      .text-section h2 {
        font-size: 2em;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #ffdddd;
      }

      .text-section p {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: white;
      }

      .button {
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #0d5ba4;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .button:hover {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
      }
    </style>
  </div>
</div>